    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><div class=\"float-clear\"></div><div><div class=\"rd__wrp-image relative\">\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/5etools-mirror-2/5etools-img/main/bestiary/BGG/Firegaunt.webp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n\t\t\t\t<img class=\"rd__image\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/5etools-mirror-2/5etools-img/main/bestiary/BGG/Firegaunt.webp\" />\n\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t</div></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>A fire giant whose burning hatred prevents it from moving on to the afterlife rises as a firegaunt. Spawned from deep rancor, the firegaunt seeks out living creatures to destroy. Like a specter, it doesn't seek redemption; it just hopes to cause as much destruction as possible before attaining its final oblivion.</p><p>A firegaunt looks like a severely burned corpse. Supernatural crimson flames flow through its veins, erupting from its wounds and its mouth.</p></div>",
